Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.63,0:23:33.81,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}今書き換えられる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.35,0:22:28.57,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}扣上枷鎖的視野如此無情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.09,0:22:37.45,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}十二條支配無法逃脫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.96,0:22:45.92,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}祈求得以安息的明日
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.70,0:22:54.93,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}手中的至愛流向事象的地平
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.38,0:23:03.99,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}囚禁的盟約  顯現偽證的輪廓
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.99,0:23:12.89,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}生命的天地  刻上盲目的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.13,0:23:15.44,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}展翅而飛Butterfly
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.44,0:23:17.93,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}奇跡的Butterfly
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.41,0:23:21.81,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}全都為你獻上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.92,0:23:24.29,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}淚水的Butterfly
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.29,0:23:26.38,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}耀眼的Butterfly
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.38,0:23:29.63,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}這一切——
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.63,0:23:33.81,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}現在都將改寫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,---TEXT---
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.75,0:00:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣繼續依賴著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.64,0:00:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被拋棄而死去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.80,0:00:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4天後  8月15日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.89,0:00:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的死被這個世界所決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.84,0:00:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不可避免的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.07,0:00:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那種事情我可不幹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.96,0:00:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要反抗世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.15,0:00:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會救出真由理
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.11,0:00:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投幣式儲物櫃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.23,0:00:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「大樓」前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.57,0:00:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,IBN5100
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.69,0:02:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡部  怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.78,0:02:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  用這個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.40,0:02:49.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.51,0:02:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,IBN5100在投幣儲物櫃裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.36,0:02:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萌郁坦白的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.21,0:02:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有被回收的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.13,0:03:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.03,0:03:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼好說的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.30,0:03:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這東西撬開櫃子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.22,0:03:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點  你好好回想一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.50,0:03:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.16,0:03:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到現在為止的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.30,0:03:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管取消了很多D-Mail
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.32,0:03:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你仍未能得到IBN5100
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.16,0:03:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概  只要你不回到原來的世界線上去就不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.37,0:03:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後  為此只能按照順序來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.53,0:03:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明已經近在眼前了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.16,0:03:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少我們抓到了線索
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.07,0:03:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐生萌郁的話  會聽從那個叫FB的人的命令對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.79,0:03:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人就是Rounder的指揮官對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.80,0:03:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.91,0:04:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要監視著IBN5100  也許就能夠和她接觸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.33,0:04:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.03,0:04:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…想見FB
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.13,0:04:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是不想見嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.54,0:04:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許見了面會讓你異常失望之類的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.42,0:04:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想瞭解…真相
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.20,0:04:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你瞭解了又要怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.04,0:04:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.68,0:04:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為我會和你一起行動嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.30,0:04:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  也不是無法交流的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.92,0:04:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.48,0:04:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.46,0:04:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和桐生萌郁在一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.31,0:05:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會那樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.83,0:05:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  那個人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.96,0:05:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之就是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.14,0:05:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一有動靜我就會聯繫你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.72,0:05:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  等等  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.75,0:05:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.67,0:05:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小岡倫？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.46,0:05:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.56,0:05:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.69,0:05:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得最近  和小岡倫都沒怎麼說過話的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.59,0:05:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.82,0:05:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小綯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.57,0:05:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘟嘟嚕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.65,0:05:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,助手姐姐  嘟嘟嚕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.21,0:05:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是紅莉栖姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.13,0:05:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好  昨天真對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.52,0:05:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴岡部  房租漲5000
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.18,0:05:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.37,0:06:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來那傢伙今天沒見到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.01,0:06:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體搞壞了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.20,0:06:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然俗話說傻瓜不會得感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.82,0:06:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他好像在到處搜集用來實驗的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.74,0:06:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實驗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.51,0:06:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是幸福的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.73,0:06:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,區區一個學生居然能租個大房子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.46,0:06:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有像你們這樣的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.81,0:06:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起想做什麼就做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.34,0:06:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.19,0:06:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.79,0:06:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  要是不快點的話限時大減價就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.40,0:06:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  走吧綯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.16,0:06:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.01,0:06:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜  姐姐們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.62,0:06:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.25,0:06:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚飯你想吃什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.97,0:06:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  什麼呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.61,0:06:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FB的簡訊嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.52,0:06:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.28,0:06:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看看行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.73,0:07:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「M4的判斷我認為是正確的」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.30,0:07:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「說實話  沒有人幹得比M4更賣力」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.42,0:07:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,M4？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.09,0:07:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FB給我起的行動代號
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.25,0:07:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有FB和我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.00,0:07:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.34,0:07:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「你的確不擅長和別人打交道  M4」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.49,0:07:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「但那不也是你的個性嗎？」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.44,0:07:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.40,0:08:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  IBN5100
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.90,0:08:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  那傢伙就是FB？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.80,0:08:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.31,0:08:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FB是個女的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.30,0:08:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.79,0:09:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.82,0:09:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.12,0:09:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後我會解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.70,0:09:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr.布朗…？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.47,0:10:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便問一下你的駕駛經驗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.76,0:10:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紙上駕照
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.28,0:10:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託開穩一點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.75,0:10:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對那個男的有印象嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.13,0:10:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒見過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.82,0:10:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.65,0:10:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4天後  8月15日
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.68,0:10:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的死被這個世界所決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.68,0:10:40.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不可避免的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.97,0:11:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛往法國的航班
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.15,0:11:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SERN所在國嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.32,0:11:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來像是FB的女人沒出現呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.32,0:11:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少聯繫一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.34,0:11:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.72,0:11:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.88,0:11:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.03,0:11:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對真由理…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.79,0:11:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  好像很久都沒和她說過話了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.66,0:11:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子也這麼說過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.59,0:11:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.18,0:11:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.59,0:11:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有直接去找他問了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.20,0:12:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問他是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.44,0:12:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去問那個我們都很熟的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.12,0:12:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦  這麼一大早的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.86,0:12:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？  先進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.39,0:12:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.41,0:12:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻就來付上漲的6000日元租金了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.08,0:12:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  這裡你應該吐槽說「是不是多了1000日元啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.24,0:12:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事情想問您
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.17,0:12:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼啊  這麼一本正經地…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.62,0:12:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認識一個名叫「FB」的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.52,0:12:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們全都看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.74,0:12:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,IBN5100從這裡被搬出去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.21,0:13:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是想要你怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.62,0:13:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只是想見到FB
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.28,0:13:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請告訴我們  她究竟在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.44,0:13:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像背叛了啊  M4
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.61,0:13:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FB為我取的行動代號
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.77,0:13:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是只有FB和我才知道的秘密…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.76,0:13:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.61,0:13:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.54,0:13:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(350,325)\fscy80\fscx80\}Ferdinand  Braun
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.54,0:13:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們知道「費迪南德·布朗」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.04,0:13:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是發明了布朗管的諾貝爾物理學獎得主
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.36,0:13:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名不虛傳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.78,0:13:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的頭文字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.15,0:13:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,F…B？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.55,0:13:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  你就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.22,0:13:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是  騙人的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.21,0:13:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依賴之後又開始逃避現實嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.00,0:13:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綯在睡覺  換個地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.56,0:14:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個城市也在不斷地發生變化
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.57,0:14:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是  FB？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.98,0:14:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.37,0:14:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  簡訊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.51,0:14:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是我寫的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.96,0:14:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會用女性用語嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.16,0:14:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是為了欺騙你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.93,0:14:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.41,0:14:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.99,0:14:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對別的人也都
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.98,0:14:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假扮成他所期望的人物形象來發簡訊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.60,0:14:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.01,0:14:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你這樣的傢伙最好騙了  真是幫大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.71,0:14:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼和她斷絕聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.57,0:14:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到IBN5100的時候那傢伙就已經沒用了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.19,0:14:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就捨棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.46,0:14:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過廣告簡訊來召集成員
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.27,0:14:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的傢伙們也方便差遣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.62,0:14:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用完之後也很好處理
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.19,0:14:56.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是原本就沒有容身之地的傢伙們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.46,0:14:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到你居然是SERN的走狗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.70,0:14:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走狗？哼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.19,0:15:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈴羽…橋田鈴女士
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.51,0:15:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是為了讓你幹這些事而照顧你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.63,0:15:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼會知道鈴女士的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.34,0:15:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這和鈴女士沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.94,0:15:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和鈴女士沒有任何關係
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.98,0:15:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.83,0:15:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們又知道些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.60,0:15:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們有在寒冬的下水道裡面睡過覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.69,0:15:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候我還是個孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.74,0:15:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混凝土可真是冷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.54,0:15:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚴寒入骨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.87,0:15:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連續三四天什麼都沒有吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.71,0:15:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要一躺下  它們就會過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.85,0:15:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老鼠會把你誤認為屍體  來咬你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.09,0:15:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.97,0:15:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼前出現了一根絲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.32,0:16:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜘蛛絲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.37,0:16:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就只能去爬了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.06,0:16:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算那前方會讓雙手沾滿污穢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.10,0:16:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那樣沿著絲往上爬著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.63,0:16:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回過神來發現自己已經是牽線木偶了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.20,0:16:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法逃脫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.59,0:16:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斷了線的木偶…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.55,0:17:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賜背叛者以死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.55,0:17:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然完成任務後也一樣會被消除
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.21,0:17:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說了我是「走狗」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.76,0:17:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不是什麼狗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.80,0:17:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是家畜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.88,0:17:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也曾想過要逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.90,0:17:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的我也有了重要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.84,0:17:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想把她捲進來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.42,0:17:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.84,0:17:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失敗是絕對不被允許的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.35,0:17:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要逃跑的話  連家人也會…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.54,0:17:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.99,0:17:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是綯對此一無所知
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.46,0:18:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.42,0:18:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.38,0:18:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡…岡部…君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.35,0:18:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡…部…君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.11,0:18:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.33,0:18:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不…起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.98,0:19:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡…岡部  手機！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.95,0:19:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D-Mail  岡部！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.07,0:19:15.03,mail,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收信人  M4\N停止搜索IBN5100\N原地待命不要擅自行動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.72,0:19:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萌郁？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.79,0:19:35.22,mail,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發信人：閃光的指壓師\NIBN5100暫時不需要了\N萌郁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.62,0:19:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.13,0:19:42.81,mail,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上司命令我停止行動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.12,0:19:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  我是漆原
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.12,0:19:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  凶真…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.93,0:19:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  IBN5100？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.82,0:19:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.24,0:19:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.83,0:20:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿至
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.81,0:20:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橋田的話不在哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.53,0:20:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說了要去CM嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.66,0:20:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了  請聽一下我的請求吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.16,0:00:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.31,0:20:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.42,0:20:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要避免真由理死亡的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.47,0:20:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要從我們現在所處的α世界線中脫出
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.92,0:20:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往岡部發送第一封D-Mail之前的世界線
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.04,0:20:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,——β世界線才行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.24,0:20:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此只有刪除在SERN的資料庫裡的資料
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.39,0:20:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由氏會死之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.02,0:20:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿萬音氏是未來人而且是我的女兒之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.88,0:20:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果全都是妄想的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.49,0:20:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小岡倫我覺得你能當輕小說作家了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.48,0:20:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是真的就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.45,0:20:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牧瀨氏你信嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.28,0:20:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為假設來說還是可信的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.95,0:20:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的話還真想要些客觀的資料
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.23,0:20:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個實在是沒可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.69,0:20:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所製作出來的時間跳躍機器的質量非常可靠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.34,0:21:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  是  是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.76,0:21:04.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是理所當然的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.78,0:21:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.09,0:21:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.01,0:21:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.60,0:21:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.55,0:21:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.54,0:21:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連接好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.59,0:21:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須要搞清楚設置才行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.40,0:21:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但10分鐘內應該能完成
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.91,0:21:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了  超級嗨客
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.55,0:21:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是超級駭客
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.63,0:21:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一封D-Mail嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.64,0:21:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是指那封吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.08,0:21:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說我被捅了還是什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.78,0:21:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是你就打算摸我的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.14,0:21:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今為止的D-Mail全都被取消
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.05,0:21:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將世界線返回原樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.43,0:21:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡是——
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.12,0:21:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SERN支配世界的反烏托邦不會出現的世界線
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.35,0:21:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理不會死亡的世界線
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.31,0:22:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後  在那條世界線上…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.29,0:22:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牧瀨紅莉栖會——
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.83,0:22:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死去


